      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/turkey-s-bear-market-on-the-mend-as-investors-wager-on-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其股市是下半年全球表现最差的股市之一，但随着基金经理押注降息即将到来，土耳其股市的命运已经开始转变。]]></description>
